CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772273110
OL,3,C'Remarkable' new drug shows signs of
OL,4,Ctreating advanced prostate cancer
OL,6,FA drug for advanced prostate cancer
OL,7,Fhas shown "remarkable" results in an
OL,8,Fearly-stage trial, with patients who
OL,9,Fhad previously stopped being receptive
OL,10,Fto treatment finding their tumours
OL,11,Fshrinking, researchers said.
OL,13,FThe treatment, a type of immunotherapy
OL,14,Fwhich harnesses the body's immune
OL,15,Fsystem to fight cancer, was found to
OL,16,Fshrink tumours or halt their growth.
OL,26,@oD@KOUoD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772273110
OL,3,C'Remarkable' new drug shows signs of
OL,4,Ctreating advanced prostate cancer
OL,6,FThe news was welcomed by cancer
OL,7,Fexperts who said that until now,
OL,8,Fprostate cancer has seen little
OL,9,Fbenefit from immunotherapies as they
OL,10,Fhave not shown much benefit in
OL,11,Fshrinking tumours and patients have
OL,12,Fexperienced severe side-effects.
OL,14,FBut the new drug, known as VIR-5500,
OL,15,Fuses a so-called cloaking device and
OL,16,Fonly activates when it reaches the
OL,17,Ftumour, minimising the risk of side-
OL,18,Feffects.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772273110
OL,3,C'Remarkable' new drug shows signs of
OL,4,Ctreating advanced prostate cancer
OL,6,FReporting their findings at the
OL,7,FAmerican Society of Clinical Oncology
OL,8,F(ASCO) Genitourinary Cancers
OL,9,FSymposium, researchers described how
OL,10,Fthe drugs was tested on 58 men with
OL,11,Fadvanced prostate cancer that had
OL,12,Fstopped responding to other treatments.
OL,14,FAlmost half (45%) of 11 patients saw
OL,15,Ftheir tumour shrink, found the
OL,16,Fresearch team, led by Professor Johann
OL,17,Fde Bono at The Institute of Cancer
OL,18,FResearch (ICR), London, and the Royal
OL,19,FMarsden NHS Foundation Trust.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772273110
OL,3,C'Remarkable' new drug shows signs of
OL,4,Ctreating advanced prostate cancer
OL,6,FMeanwhile, 88% of all the patients,
OL,7,Fwho were recruited from eight sites
OL,8,Faround the world, only experienced
OL,9,Fvery mild side effects.
OL,11,FResearchers presented details of
OL,12,Fspecific cases to the conference,
OL,13,Fincluding a 63-year-old man whose
OL,14,Fcancer had spread to his liver.
OL,16,FSome 14 cancerous liver lesions were
OL,17,F"completely resolved" after six cycles
OL,18,Fof treatment.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
