PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772273110
OL,3,C'Remarkable' new drug shows signs of
OL,4,Ctreating advanced prostate cancer
OL,6,FA 70-year-old whose cancer had spread
OL,7,Foutside the prostate saw a "complete
OL,8,Fresolution" of these additional small
OL,9,Ftumours and reported that he was
OL,10,Fenjoying an "excellent" quality of
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, a 77-year-old man involved
OL,14,Fin the study had "undetectable" levels
OL,15,Fof PSA after 17 cycles of treatment.
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@KO]rD@MOUrD@WO]vD@ROUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
