PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772273110
OL,3,C'Remarkable' new drug shows signs of
OL,4,Ctreating advanced prostate cancer
OL,6,FOf the 17 patients who were given the
OL,7,Fhighest dose of the drug, half (53%)
OL,8,Fsaw their levels of prostate-specific
OL,9,Fantigen (PSA), a blood marker which
OL,10,Findicates prostate disease, drop by
OL,11,F90%. And 82% saw their PSA levels
OL,12,Fhalve.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
