PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772273110
OL,3,C'Remarkable' new drug shows signs of
OL,4,Ctreating advanced prostate cancer
OL,6,F"Pending further clinical validation,
OL,7,Favailable data are suggestive of a
OL,8,Fgenerally favourable safety profile,
OL,9,Fwith evidence of meaningful anti-
OL,10,Ftumour activity," according to the
OL,11,Fabstract presented at the conference.
OL,13,FThe drug is called a "T-cell engager"
OL,14,Fand works by binding to the body's
OL,15,Fimmune T-cells and to a protein found
OL,16,Fon the surface of prostate cancer
OL,17,Fcells.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@QO]uD@VOUuD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1772273110
OL,3,C'Remarkable' new drug shows signs of
OL,4,Ctreating advanced prostate cancer
OL,6,FWhen it binds to the cancer cells,
OL,7,Fwherever they are in the body, it
OL,8,Fbrings the T-cells into contact with
OL,9,Fthem, enabling the attack.
OL,11,FThe ICR said VIR-5500 also contains a
OL,12,F"cloaking device" which keeps it
OL,13,Finactive until it reaches the
OL,14,Fcancerous cell ` which helps to
OL,15,Fprevent side-effects from occurring.
OL,17,FThis also enables the drug to stay in
OL,18,Fthe blood stream for longer, meaning
OL,19,Ffewer doses may need to be given to
OL,20,Fpatients, according to the study,
OL,21,Fwhich was funded by Vir Biotechnology.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@QO]
