OL,3,C'Remarkable' new drug shows signs of
OL,4,Ctreating advanced prostate cancer
OL,6,FThe study was a phase 1 trial looks at
OL,7,Fthe safety and efficacy of the drug
OL,8,Fbefore it is tested on a wider group.
